column4: Your account address copied from your polkadot.js browser extension.
column5: Your Binance Smart Chain address. You can also use your Ethereum ERC20 address, just note that you will receive USDT on the Binance Smart Chain not the Ethereum network.
column6: How many A seed coupons would you like? Note that each coupon will incur a 2000 COFFEE debt that needs to be paid off before the end of the contest.
column7: How many B seed coupons would you like? Note that each coupon will incur a 1000 COFFEE debt that needs to be paid off before the end of the contest.
column8: How many C seed coupons would you like? Note that each coupon will incur 500 COFFEE debt that needs to be paid off before the end of the contest.
